journalist.

55
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:37,800
Here, a loquat as reward.

56
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,120
Yu.

57
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:45,960
I have something to tell you.

58
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:48,800
Come closer.

59
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,360
