66
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,520
Cockroach?

67
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,320
I took it out.

68
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,000
Do you like it?

69
00:06:46,870 --> 00:06:48,120
I've always liked it.

70
